	(text "J1 Thermal Switch - connects to X-Eng dual termal switch.  Active Low to enable\nJ2 Supply - Connects to the vehicle Switch Voltage\nJ4 Expansion - connects to teh Gauge extension module \nJ5 FanPower - BlowerFanEnable is a 12V supply for the heater blower.  Can be connected to the B connection of the Blower Switch\n         - LowFanSupply connects to the radiator Fan\n         - HighFanSupply connects to the Air Conditioning Cooler Fan\n"
